response.overview: In director Baz Luhrmann's contemporary take on William Shakespeare's classic tragedy, the Montagues and Capulets have moved their ongoing feud to the sweltering suburb of Verona Beach, where Romeo and Juliet fall in love and secretly wed. Though the film is visually modern, the bard's dialogue remains.
response.tagline: My only love sprung from my only hate.
response.title: Romeo + Juliet

results.name: Why Leonardo DiCaprio was the perfect Romeo | A Life In Pictures | BAFTA
